## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/hungoffoperandtraits">HungoffOperandTraits</a> - determine the allocation regime of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/use">Use</a> array when it is not a prefix to the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/user">User</a> object, but allocated at an unrelated heap address.

This is the traits class that is needed when the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/use">Use</a> array must be resizable.
